{"type": "article", "id": 2706, "title": "便携式咖啡机", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-08T07:43:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232445DaenLzs8ErcAPYyZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t徒步旅行、露营或者在宾馆休息，能喝上一杯浓缩咖啡该是多么惬意。日前，WACACO 就推出了一款名为“ minipresso ”的便携式咖啡机。Minipresso 的便携性在于其独特的产品构想，瓶子上下两端分别加装咖啡粉和开水，无需电源供电，凭借半自动活塞产生的压力将开水挤压到咖啡过滤器中，从而萃取出浓缩咖啡，用户根据按压活塞的次数控制饮用量。整个制作过程不需要任何电力装置。原价 49 美元（现促销价 39 美元），<a href=\"http://www.wacaco.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232444EfIWQAGk9Lj1vrNe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232444rPOzawxFs1de7Afb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232444q6h1JDpWEfIANlok.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232445yj39qZi6aO5zE17g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5390625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}